  "anticipated_spec_changes": "We are making changes to the following specs:\n\n- Service Worker Spec\nhttps://github.com/w3c/ServiceWorker/pull/1769 has already been merged\n\n- Resource timing spec\nhttps://github.com/w3c/resource-timing/pull/415 has been reviewed, and are waiting for merge (waiting for the fetch-spec changes to be reviewed)\n\n- Fetch Spec\nhttps://github.com/whatwg/fetch/pull/1832 has been reviewed, but are still waiting for editor's review and are also waiting for other vendor's signal.",
